    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526256262350-7da7584cf5eb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1050&q=80" alt="Healed by Helping" />
    
    <h1>Healed by Helping</h1>
    <p>
      After battling depression and anxiety, Meera Sharma found herself in a dark place with no clear path forward. One day, she volunteered at a shelter and helped a young girl find her lost mother. That moment of connection sparked something deep within her.
    </p>
    <p>
      Meera began dedicating her time to helping others—counseling teens, organizing support groups, and spreading mental health awareness. Through helping others heal, she found her own strength. Today, she’s a certified therapist and motivational speaker, living proof that the best way to heal is often to help.
    </p>

